   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To my lord brother Isidoros, Kollouthos, greeting. It is not a good thing you do in being unwilling to send the wages for threshing(?) through Aloabai; nor have you delivered the full amount of barley.  . . . be so good as to come up secretly with them. It is a good moment.;(2nd hand) I pray for your continued good health.;;(Verso) (Christian symbol) To Isidoros.</ab>
         </div>
